casebody.data:
James PERRY v. J. W. HUNDLEY et al. No. 318. Circuit Court of Appeals, Tenth Circuit. July 12, 1930. Mansfield, Brunson, Kemp & Ahrens, of Ada, Okl., for appellant. Harrell & Kerr, of Ada, Okl., for appellees.

Before LEWIS, PHILLIPS, and McDERMOTT, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Appeal dismissed July 12, 1930, on joint motion of appellant and appellees.
